Hey Jason, in the CSS you need to set a width for your theme, then set margin-left: auto; and then margin-right: auto; this should centre it for you... for example my theme uses #pagelayout (yours may well be called something else) as the wrapper so... 
```text
#pagelayout {

 width:960px;

 margin-left:auto;

 margin-right:auto;

}

Hope this helps.
```

